{"tid":2044164,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本港建基因數據庫　料助罕見病患者","createTime":"2020-05-31T02:40:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T03:05:10.000Z","uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3fe291f813c95021e54ada0165056e7366912355","tid":2044164,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T02:40:20.000Z","msg":"極權政府開始收集人民嘅DNA了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】本港基因研究目前只能參考外國數據，基因組醫學督導委員會、食物及衞生局副秘書長方毅相信，能幫助罕見病患者。<br />\n<br />\n方毅：「基因組的參考，其參考點七成的基因都來至白人，所以我們都需要本地人口的數據庫，讓我們的參考點準確一些。參考點準確的話，我們將來可能發展個人化及精準醫學診斷，及治療的方案，可能這樣才能夠針對性幫助個別特別的病人。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=392798\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392798&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdEBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=fc315c8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392798&h=a6f0266f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=392798</a>"},{"pid":"068fd0eb6a967069676c8547d0a5da4f6559726e","tid":2044164,"uid":73856,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T02:41:04.000Z","msg":"隨時幫中共權貴換器官"},{"pid":"33e967366905cce0c04806887fa9cde1d1d8a5ad","tid":2044164,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T02:42:00.000Z","msg":"人體鍊成嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9378536a4e520afef6d29912bd0800ece90e7117","tid":2044164,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"068fd0eb6a967069676c8547d0a5da4f6559726e","tid":2044164,"uid":73856,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T02:41:04.000Z","msg":"隨時幫中共權貴換器官"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T02:49:38.000Z","msg":"佢哋喺再教育營搵可能仲快，始終搞咗咁多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8884dfbcecc97d79780a35247ce4ff4c135e